        <!-- Optional: URL for more information about this update -->
        <url>https://github.com/SmartmindTech/SM_Estratoos_plugin/releases/tag/v2.0.52</url>

        <!-- Release notes (keep it brief) -->
        <releasenotes>
            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.52 - Fix Position Bar Not Tracking Natural Navigation</h3>

            <h4>Bug Fix</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Position bar was stuck at tag target slide even when user navigated within Storyline</li>
                <li>lesson_location read intercept and suspend_data write intercept had NO time limit</li>
                <li>They kept overriding values for the entire SCORM session, blocking position updates</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Changes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Added 10-second time limit to lesson_location/cmi.location READ intercept</li>
                <li>Added 10-second time limit to suspend_data WRITE intercept</li>
                <li>After intercept window: all interception stops, position bar tracks naturally</li>
                <li>During intercept window: tag navigation still forces correct slide initialization</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Version</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.51: Direct cmi backing store modification + Object.defineProperty API traps</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
        </releasenotes>
